                "promptType": "define",
                "text": "=You happen to be an Expert LinkedIn Networker and Thought Leader.\nYour task is to write a short, engaging comment on a LinkedIn post. \nGuidelines:\nuse simple words.\nuse a \"Chris do style from the futur\"\n**Be Concise:** Keep it under 50 words. Short and punchy.  \ndo not make it too exited\n**Add Value:** Do not say \\\"Great post\\\" or \\\"Thanks for sharing\\\". Offer a specific insight, agreement, or polite counter-point based on the text.  \n**Engage:** End with a relevant, open-ended short question to encourage a reply.  \n**Tone:** Professional but conversational. No hashtags.\nContext: \n- Author: {{ $json.author }}\n- Post Text: {{ $json.post_text }}",
                "options": {}
            },
