                "text": "📢 #Internship Summer 2023 📢\n\nCurrently, in my last year (5th year) apprentice engineering program in #DevOps, I have the opportunity to realize at least an 8 opportunity week internship internationally. I'm looking for an internship as a #DevOpsEngineer or as a #SoftwareEngineer from June 2023 for a period between 2 and 3 months.\n\nFeel free to contact me should you require any further information and don’t hesitate to share this post 😁",
